com.polarion.alm.shared.api.model.document

Interface DocumentSelector<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelObjectSelector<T,DocumentSelector<T>,DocumentReference>

    public interface DocumentSelector<T>
extends ModelObjectSelector<T,DocumentSelector<T>,DocumentReference>
    Interface for selecting the document using optional revision and mandatory project id document path or space path and document name. The selection is finished by using path(String), projectSpaceAndName(String, String, String) or spaceReferenceAndName(SpaceReference, String) method and the selector object cannot be used anymore after that.
    Since:
    3.9.0
